  "prompt": "I want to read about Swami Vivekananda. Tell me one or two good books on Swami Vivekananda?",
  "response": "Certainly! Two highly regarded books on Swami Vivekananda that provide valuable insights into his life, philosophy, and teachings are:\n\n1. **\"Vivekananda: A Biography\" by Swami Nikhilananda** - This biography offers a detailed account of Vivekananda's life, his spiritual journey, and his impact on both Indian and Western thought. It provides context to his teachings and the historical background of his time.\n\n2. **\"The Complete Works of Swami Vivekananda\"** - This multi-volume set includes all of Vivekananda's writings, lectures, and addresses. It is an essential collection for anyone looking to deeply understand his philosophy and ideas. \n\nBoth of these works can help you appreciate the contributions of Swami Vivekananda to spirituality and philosophy.",
